function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	idCloneTorlos = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_questgiver, true)
	idCloneHuma = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_Huma, true)
	idCloneCharthi = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_Charthi, true)

		
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCloneCharthi) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCloneTorlos) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCloneHuma) then
	
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idCloneCharthi)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idCloneTorlos)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idCloneHuma)
		
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idCloneCharthi, loc_NPCWalkTo_03, "NPC_Walk", false)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idCloneTorlos, loc_NPCWalkTo_02, "NPC_Walk", false)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idCloneHuma, loc_NPCWalkTo_01, "NPC_Walk", false)

		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idCloneTorlos, 1.0)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idCloneHuma, 1.0)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idCloneCharthi, 1.0)
				
	end


end
